Package: clustershard
Type: Package
Title: Analyze and Cluster Compositional Pottery Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Daniel", "Helkey", email = "dhelkey@ucsc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
	person("David", "Draper", email = "draper@ucsc", role = c("ctb")),
	person("Judith", "Mauche", email = "judith@ucsc.edu", role = c("ctb")))
Description: This package provides a GUI tool to analyze elemental compositional pottery data.
    The tool simplifies the process of imporing data, perforing dimentionality reduction (through Principle
	Component Analyis), and clustering the observations (using k-means or Gaussian mixture modeling).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
